{"type":"text","timestamp":1775875278948,"sessionID":"ses_2859af2f6ffe6Dgxn0a1FnVUa2","part":{"id":"prt_d7a6a286f0016jqsqQSVfjAXJb","messageID":"msg_d7a69fe610015KWtLSS4Hi8BMW","sessionID":"ses_2859af2f6ffe6Dgxn0a1FnVUa2","type":"text","text":"I've successfully created the delta-spec.md file for **AR-016: PicoD 文件管理 API (File Management API)**.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe specification file contains:\n\n### Structure\n- **1067 lines** of comprehensive specification\n- **10 major requirements** with detailed GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios\n- **100+ acceptance scenarios** covering all file operations\n\n### Key Requirements\n1. **FileManager Interface** - Core file operations (Read, Write, Delete, List, Stat, Move, Copy)\n2. **Path Validation & Security** - Path traversal protection, symlink handling, allowed paths\n3. **File Size & Content Limits** - Configurable size limits, file type restrictions\n4. **File Streaming Support** - Large file streaming with range requests\n5. **Batch File Operations** - Efficient batch Stat/Delete/Copy operations\n6. **Sandbox Integration** - Integration with AR-009 sandbox interface\n7. **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error types for all failure scenarios\n8. **Context Cancellation** - Graceful cancellation handling\n9. **File Watching & Events** - Directory watching with event notifications\n10. **Configuration** - Environment-based configuration\n\n### New Interfaces\n- `FileManager` interface with 18 methods\n- Complete file types (`FileInfo`, `FileContent`, `DirectoryListing`, etc.)\n- Error types specific to file operations\n- Configuration types for file manager\n\n### File Created\n📄 `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-016/delta-spec.md`","time":{"start":1775875278944,"end":1775875278944}}}
